The '''Faculdade de Teologia Metodista Livre''' (Free Methodist College), also known as '''FTML''' or simply '''Metodista''', is a private [[school]] based primarily in [[São Paulo]], [[Brazil]].
==History== Metodista traces its history to 1956, when the [[Free Methodist Church|Methodists]] created the [[Free Methodist Church]] (and the Theology College) in São Paulo.
==Graduation programs== The school offers three degree programs at its São Paulo campus: * Doctorate (Ph.D. / Th.D.) * Master's degree * Bachelor's degree (Theology)
